.
.br
Aborts a currently running test
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-clients\fR:
.
.br
List available clients (slaves and monitors) on master process
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-collect\fR:
.
.br
Get\'s report for specifed test
