.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-run\fR:
.
.br
Runs a test package on master process
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-slave\fR:
.
.br
Spawns a slave server process
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-tests\fR:
.
.br
List all available test packages on master process
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fBstage\-uninstall\fR:
.
.br
Uninstalls a test package on master process
.
.IP "" 0
